markets.title: Will Zendaya attend Kai Cenat’s ‘Mafiathon 3’ Stream?
markets.rules_primary: If Zendaya attends Kai Cenat’s ‘Mafiathon 3’ Stream, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: For the purposes of this market, the individual must be physically present with Kai Cenat during the Mafiathon 3 live stream and appear on camera in real time. Remote appearances, including FaceTime, Zoom, phone calls, or any other form of video or audio communication, will not count. Similarly, pre-recorded videos, shout-outs, or clips will not satisfy the requirement for an appearance.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs
